data.comment: The first-half is just kicking off.
Throw-in for Falkenbergs in their own half.
In the minute 2, Falkenbergs awarded a free kick in their own half.
Malmo pushes forward through Anders Christiansen, whose finish on goal is saved.
Falkenbergs's John Bjorkengren breaks free at Stadion. But the strike goes wide of the post.
In the minute 3, Bojan Pandzic awards Malmo a goal kick.
Falkenbergs have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
Corner awarded to Malmo.
In the minute 7, In Malmo a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Malmo have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
Corner awarded to Malmo.
In the minute 9, Oscar Lewicki (Malmo) gets up for a header but cannot keep the ball on target.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Malmo.
Malmo drive forward at breakneck speed but are pulled up for offside.
In the minute 11, Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Malmo in their own half.
Goal kick for Falkenbergs at Stadion.
Throw-in Falkenbergs.
In the minute 13, Free kick for Falkenbergs in the half of Malmo.
In Malmo, Falkenbergs push forward quickly but are pulled up for offside.
Ball safe as Malmo is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 15, Throw-in for Falkenbergs close to the penalty box.
Free kick for Malmo in their own half.
Bojan Pandzic signals a Falkenbergs throw-in in Malmo's half.
In the minute 16, Falkenbergs attack but Gustaf Nilsson's header doesn't find the target.
Malmo have a goal kick.
Throw-in for Malmo at Stadion.
In the minute 17, Can Falkenbergs capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Malmo's half?
Falkenbergs have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
Malmo are caught offside.
In the minute 19, Malmo awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Malmo push forward at Stadion and Amin Sarr gets in a strike. This is blocked, however, by a determined Falkenbergs defence.
Throw-in for Malmo in the half of Falkenbergs.
In the minute 20, Free kick Malmo.
Malmo surge into the attack at Stadion but Amin Sarr’s header is off-target.
Ball goes out of play for a Falkenbergs goal kick.
In the minute 21, Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Malmo in their own half.
Throw-in high up the field for Malmo in Malmo.
Isaac Thelin (Malmo) fires in a shot – and hits the post!
In the minute 23, Bojan Pandzic awards the away team a throw-in.
Falkenbergs have a goal kick.
Corner awarded to Malmo.
In the minute 26, Bojan Pandzic awards Falkenbergs a goal kick.
Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Falkenbergs.
Falkenbergs have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
In the minute 30, Malmo are whistled for offside.
Bojan Pandzic awards the home team a throw-in.
Malmo have a dangerous throw-in.
In the minute 32, Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Malmo.
Corner awarded to Malmo.
Free kick for Malmo in the half of Falkenbergs.
In the minute 35, Malmo drives forward and Anders Christiansen gets in a shot. Without netting, however.
Corner awarded to Malmo.
Malmo have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
In the minute 35, Ball goes out of play for a Falkenbergs goal kick.
Free kick for Malmo in their own half.
Falkenbergs awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 37, Can Malmo get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Falkenbergs's half?
Goal kick for Falkenbergs at Stadion.
Falkenbergs to take a throw-in in Malmo territory.
In the minute 39, Can Falkenbergs capitalize from this dangerous free kick?
At Stadion, Eric Larsson has been yellow-carded for the home team.
Play has been interrupted briefly in Malmo to check on Tobias Englund, who is grimacing with pain.
In the minute 40, Tobias Englund returns to the field for Falkenbergs after picking up a slight injury.
Goal! Soren Rieks gives Malmo a 1-0 lead.
Great play from Fouad Bachirou to set up the goal.
In the minute 42, It's a goal kick for the home team in Malmo.
A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
Malmo awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 43, Can Malmo get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Falkenbergs's half?
Soren Rieks is down and play has been interrupted for a few moments.
At Stadion the fourth official shows that 2 minutes will be added to the 1st half.
In the minute 45, Corner awarded to Falkenbergs.
Falkenbergs push upfield but Bojan Pandzic quickly pulls them for offside.
At Stadion, Malmo are penalized for being offside.
In the minute 45, Free kick for Malmo in their own half.
Malmo’s Soren Rieks is on his feet again at Stadion.
Bojan Pandzic blows to end the first-half.
In the minute 46, The second half has started at Stadion.
Bojan Pandzic signals a throw-in for Malmo, close to Falkenbergs's area.
Ball safe as Falkenbergs is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 46, Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Falkenbergs in their own half.
Goal kick for Malmo at Stadion.
Malmo are coming forward and Amin Sarr gets in a strike, it misses the target, however.
In the minute 49, It's a goal kick for the away team in Malmo.
Falkenbergs to take a throw-in in Malmo territory.
Falkenbergs's Gustaf Nilsson is on target but unsuccessful.
In the minute 51, It's now 2-0 in Malmo as Isaac Thelin scores for Malmo.
Amin Sarr with an assist there.
In Malmo a free kick has been awarded the away team.
In the minute 53, Franz Brorsson (Malmo) has received a yellow card from Bojan Pandzic.
Falkenbergs advance rapidly upfield but Bojan Pandzic blows for offside.
Free kick Malmo.
In the minute 57, Throw-in for Malmo in the half of Falkenbergs.
Falkenbergs make their first substitution with John Chibuike replacing Marcus Mathisen.
John Chibuike (Falkenbergs) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
In the minute 59, A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
The home team replace Behrang Safari with Jonas Knudsen.
Jon Dahl Tomasson is making the team's second substitution at Stadion with Arnor Traustason replacing Soren Rieks.
In the minute 59, Felix Beijmo is replacing Eric Larsson for the home team.
In Malmo a free kick has been awarded the away team.
In the minute 60, Bojan Pandzic awards Malmo a goal kick.
Felix Beijmo for Malmo has been booked by Bojan Pandzic and receives a first yellow card.
Malmo push upfield but Bojan Pandzic quickly pulls them for offside.
Malmo have a goal kick.
In the minute 63, Throw-in for Malmo at Stadion.
Gustaf Nilsson (Falkenbergs) is first to the ball but his header is off-target.
Ball goes out of play for a Malmo goal kick.
In the minute 65, Bojan Pandzic signals a Falkenbergs throw-in in Malmo's half.
Throw-in for Falkenbergs in the half of Malmo.
Gustaf Nilsson (Falkenbergs) strikes at Stadion but his header is cleared.
In the minute 67, Important block from the Falkenbergs defence as Amin Sarr fires in a strike for Malmo.
The away team have replaced Karl Soderstrom with Edi Sylisufaj. This is the second substitution made today by Hans Eklund.
Malmo have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
In the minute 68, Amin Sarr (Malmo) strikes – and hits the bar! Ohhhh so close!
Corner awarded to Malmo.
Malmo's Amin Sarr gets his shot away but it misses the target.
In the minute 69, Ball goes out of play for a Falkenbergs goal kick.
Falkenbergs awarded a free kick in their own half.
Free kick for Malmo in their own half.
In the minute 72, Falkenbergs's Edi Sylisufaj goes close with his head but his effort is blocked.
Free kick for Malmo in the half of Falkenbergs.
Malmo's Isaac Thelin gets in a shot on goal at Stadion. But the effort is unsuccessful.
In the minute 74, Malmo have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
In Malmo Malmo drive forward through Amin Sarr. His shot is on target but it's saved.
Amin Sarr gets his shot on target but fails to score for Malmo.
In the minute 77, Malmo have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
Throw-in Falkenbergs.
In Malmo, John Bjorkengren of Falkenbergs is presented with a shooting opportunity. But the strike is blocked by the covering defence.
Corner awarded to Falkenbergs.
In the minute 79, Lorik Ademi is on a sub for Christoffer Carlsson for Falkenbergs.
The away team replace John Bjorkengren with Matthew Garbett.
In the minute 80, Malmo needs to be cautious. Falkenbergs have an attacking throw-in.
Malmo awarded a free kick in their own half.
Malmo make their fourth substitution with Adi Nalic replacing Anders Christiansen.
In the minute 80, Erdal Rakip is on a sub for Oscar Lewicki for Malmo.
Malmo have a dangerous throw-in.
Throw-in for Malmo close to the penalty box.
In the minute 83, Bojan Pandzic signals a throw-in for Malmo, close to Falkenbergs's area.
Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Falkenbergs in their own half.
In the minute 84, Throw-in for Malmo in their own half.
Adi Nalic is booked for the home team.
Malmo's Adi Nalic misses with an attempt on goal.
Bojan Pandzic awards Falkenbergs a goal kick.
In the minute 86, Falkenbergs to take a throw-in in Malmo territory.
In the minute 87, Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Malmo.
Goal! The away team reduce the deficit to 2-1 through a strike by Tobias Englund. .
That's a fine assist from Anton Wede.
Free kick for Malmo in their own half.
Isaac Thelin of Malmo smashes in a shot on target. The keeper saves, though.
Malmo have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
Bojan Pandzic will wait an extra 4 minutes before blowing the whistle to end the 2nd half.
Corner awarded to Malmo.
In Malmo, Malmo push forward quickly but are pulled up for offside.
Edi Sylisufaj for Falkenbergs drives towards goal at Stadion. But the finish is unsuccessful.
Free kick Falkenbergs.
Bojan Pandzic blows to end the match. The final score is 2-1.
Lasse Nielsen (Malmo) gets a yellow card.
